    "_comment": "=================================================================",
    "_comment2": "openvsx-sync.json — Open VSX mirror / air-gapped sync manifest",
    "_comment3": "",
    "_comment4": "Used by the `ovsx` CLI to publish or mirror extensions to a",
    "_comment5": "private Open VSX registry (e.g. for air-gapped DevSpaces clusters).",
    "_comment6": "",
    "_comment7": "Run with:",
    "_comment8": "  npx ovsx publish <vsix-file> -r <registry-url> -p <token>",
    "_comment9": "  OR feed to a mirror job:",
    "_comment10": "  ovsx mirror --extensions openvsx-sync.json -r <registry-url>",
    "_comment11": "================================================================="
  },

